Subject: cifs: initialize file_info_lock

From: Rabin Vincent <rabinv@axis.com>

commit 81ddd8c0c5e1cb41184d66567140cb48c53eb3d1 upstream.

Reviewed-by: Jeff Layton <jlayton@redhat.com>

